data.description: Lovely home with lots of room to spread out! Step inside to beautiful and easy-to-maintain vinyl wood floors throughout several living spaces on the main level. To the left is a formal dining room with lots of natural light, chair railing, and gorgeous light fixture. To the right is a bright and airy flex space with a bay window - home office, formal living, playroom, seating area, you name it! Double doors lead to a family room with cozy stone fireplace, tall vaulted ceilings, and access to a sunroom, perfect for bug free dining or lounging. Back inside, enjoy an updated kitchen featuring granite counters, breakfast bar, on-trend white cabinets, tile backsplash, double ovens, and spacious breakfast room. Laundry room and half bath complete this level. Upstairs, retreat to the oversized primary bedroom with a tray ceiling and room for a seating area as well as an en-suite bath with dual sinks, garden tub, and separate walk-in tiled shower. Three spacious secondary bedrooms and a full bath on this level ensure room for everyone! Don't miss the finished basement with a large living room with a built-in wood bar -a great space for a man cave, lounge, media room, or just extra living space. There are also two bedrooms and a full bath as well as unfinished storage. Outside, enjoy private wooded views from the massive deck on the back of the home or the covered downstairs patio with an extended patio slab. Community is on the golf course, has a pool with a lazy river, and hosts community events for residents!
